## Third-Party Licenses

This project uses several third-party libraries and tools. Below are their respective licenses:

### yt-dlp
- **License**: The Unlicense
- **Website**: https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp
- **Usage**: Core video downloading functionality

### Streamlit
- **License**: Apache License 2.0
- **Website**: https://github.com/streamlit/streamlit
- **Usage**: Web application framework

### FFmpeg
- **License**: GNU Lesser General Public License (LGPL) version 2.1
- **Website**: https://ffmpeg.org/
- **Usage**: Video processing and conversion (via ffmpeg-python)

### schedule
- **License**: MIT License
- **Website**: https://github.com/dbader/schedule
- **Usage**: Task scheduling functionality

### streamlit-calendar
- **License**: MIT License
- **Website**: https://github.com/im-perativa/streamlit-calendar
- **Usage**: Calendar widget for scheduler

### streamlit-datetime-picker
- **License**: MIT License
- **Website**: https://github.com/null-none/streamlit-datetime-picker
- **Usage**: DateTime picker widget

